<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="smile-v">smile <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /smaɪl/    美 /smaɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>微笑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They sat there <strong>smiling at</strong> each other.
他们坐在那儿对视而笑。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>以微笑表示：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She smiles her thanks.
她以微笑表示感谢。</p></div></div>